            <text>
                <body>
                    <div type="edition">
                        <div type="textpart">
                            <ab><persName><name ref="Lampertus">Lamberto</name></persName> figlio
                            <rs key="#Clerical_concubinage">della <persName
                                key="#Clerical_concubinage">fu <name ref="Sassa"
                                >Sassa</name></persName></rs> offre pro anima sua alla <rs
                            key="#Collegiate_churches">chiesa e canonica</rs> di <orgName
                            ref="#juridical_persons/242" key="#Collegiate_churches">San Pietro qui
                            dicitur Maiore</orgName> posta iusta <rs key="#Clusae/gates">porta qui
                            dicitur Sancti Petri</rs>, tres portionis de medietatem di un
                        appezzamento di terra, quod est campo, posto in loco et finibus <placeName
                            ref="#places/2120">in Limite</placeName> prope la <rs key="#Churches"
                            >chiesa</rs> di <orgName key="#Churches" ref="#juridical_persons/281"
                            >Santa Margherita</orgName>, <rs key="#Confinia #Landed_possessions"
                            >confinante</rs> uno capo in via publica, alio capo in simitula, lateras
                        ambas con terra del <persName key="#Confinia #Landed_possessions #Viscount"
                            ref="#people/3101">fu Sisemundo</persName>
                        <rs key="#Viscount">visconte</rs>, per una misura complessiva di 21 staia
                        con tutte le sue dipendenze. Chiede al <rs key="#Writer #Notary">notaio
                            imperiale</rs>
                        <persName key="#Writer #Notary"><name ref="Ildebrandus"
                            >Ildebrando</name></persName> la stesura della cartula. Actum <placeName
                            ref="#places/4">Luca</placeName>. <rs key="#Witness">Testimoni</rs>
                        sottoscrittori: <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Wido"
                            >Guido</name></persName> del <persName>fu <name ref="Aginus"
                                >Agimo</name></persName>, <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Vitus"
                                >Vito</name></persName> di <persName><name ref="Albitius"
                                >Albizio</name></persName>, <persName key="#Witness"><name
                                ref="Bellomo">Bellomo</name></persName> di <persName><name
                                ref="Beritius">Berizio</name></persName>.</ab>
                        </div>
                    </div>
